Package: cycif.importer
Title: CyCIF Analysis Pipeline for Multiplexed Tissue Imaging Data
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R:
    person("Clemens", "Hug", , "clemens.hug@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for analyzing CyCIF (Cyclic Immunofluorescence)
    multiplexed tissue imaging data. Provides functions for importing UNMICST cell
    segmentation data, applying gating thresholds, assigning regions of interest (ROIs),
    sampling cells, and generating summary statistics. Designed with a modular three-stage
    pipeline: import & gate, sample, and summarize.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
